\id EST Kyaka Enga Shorter Bible, SF codes August 20, 93
\h ESETA
\toc1 ESETA
\toc2 Eseta
\toc3 Ese
\mt1 ESETA
\ip Yuu Pesa dokona kiŋi dokona kupwa pingi yuu gii dokopa palenge anda dokona piya dokona lao arome pii mende buku Eseta dakena pyasi palamo. Juu enda mapwae Eseta lenge dokome paka napala banya wambu dupwa kondome kumuo nakamana yanda pimwai dupwame pyao kumako pyuo kareyaminyipape lete pyuo nyiyamo arome pii doko pyasi palamo.
\ip Eseta doko banya apange Motekaiya dokome dopa pinya dapa pinya lao lao kata lasaka pyuo lao roleya.
\ip Yuu gii Purimi lenge dokopa Juu wambu dupwa malu palyuo rae maiyuo karenge dokona lao polo lao pyasi palamoko.
\c 1
